{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You are a sentient fungus, reanimating the scrapped robotic body of a long-dead machine.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey with your friends to explore a world of mushrooms, blooming through the technological wreckage of a failed human civilization.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build Your Combat Style in a Classless System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/extras/MycoRelic_Steam_Gif1.gif?t=1736871830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dodge, block, parry, and engage the hostile tribes and creatures of the island. Master a variety of weapons, each with their own  move sets and statistics.  Equip yourself with armor\u00a0that suits your playstyle and aesthetic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Scavenge Parts to Enhance Your Robotic Body</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/extras/MycoRelic_Steam_Gif2.5.gif?t=1736871830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start with a decrepit, moldy frame. Replace it to overcome the dangers of the environment, support your combat style, or enhance elemental effects. Expand your stamina, boost the integrity of your frame, and increase the potency of your fungal magic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Wield the Elemental Powers of Ancient Fungi</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/extras/MycoRelic_Steam_Gif3.gif?t=1736871830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Infuse yourself using the elemental power within each fungus. Combine effects to produce explosive results. Use fire to burn your enemies and scorch a path through barricades. Cast healing water to rejuvenate your friends and block roaring flames. Call upon the spiritual essence of the world and empower your allies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Move Freely Through a Mystical Environment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump, air-dash, and mantle over obstacles. Hone your platforming skill and discover new pathways across stony cliffs, burning magma, noxious mangroves, and spore riddled chasms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play Solo or Join Your Friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cooperate with your friends to solve puzzles, defeat bosses, and clear dungeons. Join your friend's world bringing your character and items with you.\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736871830","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/page.bg.jpg?t=1736871830","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/26b020714f0105dc0237619145bb3a793ae3459c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736871830","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/26b020714f0105dc0237619145bb3a793ae3459c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736871830","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/extras/MycoRelic_Steam_Gif_Discord.gif?t=1736871830\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You are a sentient fungus, reanimating the scrapped robotic body of a long-dead machine.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey with your friends to explore a world of mushrooms, blooming through the technological wreckage of a failed human civilization.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build Your Combat Style in a Classless System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/extras/MycoRelic_Steam_Gif1.gif?t=1736871830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dodge, block, parry, and engage the hostile tribes and creatures of the island. Master a variety of weapons, each with their own  move sets and statistics.  Equip yourself with armor\u00a0that suits your playstyle and aesthetic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Scavenge Parts to Enhance Your Robotic Body</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/extras/MycoRelic_Steam_Gif2.5.gif?t=1736871830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start with a decrepit, moldy frame. Replace it to overcome the dangers of the environment, support your combat style, or enhance elemental effects. Expand your stamina, boost the integrity of your frame, and increase the potency of your fungal magic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Wield the Elemental Powers of Ancient Fungi</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/extras/MycoRelic_Steam_Gif3.gif?t=1736871830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Infuse yourself using the elemental power within each fungus. Combine effects to produce explosive results. Use fire to burn your enemies and scorch a path through barricades. Cast healing water to rejuvenate your friends and block roaring flames. Call upon the spiritual essence of the world and empower your allies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Move Freely Through a Mystical Environment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump, air-dash, and mantle over obstacles. Hone your platforming skill and discover new pathways across stony cliffs, burning magma, noxious mangroves, and spore riddled chasms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play Solo or Join Your Friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cooperate with your friends to solve puzzles, defeat bosses, and clear dungeons. Join your friend's world bringing your character and items with you.\u00a0</p>","developers":["Sandy Dingo Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624080/header.jpg?t=1736871830","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257002852,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257002852/movie480.mp4?t=1708628582","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257002852/movie_max.mp4?t=1708628582"},"name":"MycoRelic - Official Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257002852/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1708628582","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2